=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manaburn</span><hr size=1> yes, there is a space of 1 minute that each wizard has to wait after the last to manaburn the target <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.cogeco.ca/~eqhost/Santerai/wiz.JPG" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:white;font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;">63 Wizardess</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:white;font-family:verdana;font-size:xx-small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=464590" target="top">Peek Under The Robe</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=veladorn>Veladorn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<br>I have needs too!</span><br>  Posts: 1342<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/23/03 6:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manaburn</span><hr size=1> The first caster of manaburn gets a message too.  Its the warn off message.  I have my worn off messages set to be a very bright orange so I can spot them easily.  <br>
<br>
What I usually do is right after I manaburn I tell the next wizard I manaburned and will send him another tell in a minute when my MB is off.  I then do all my med tricks (harvest, harvest2, mod rod), as soon as I see that orange test saying your manaburn spell has worn off (or somethign to that effect), I tell the next wizard that its all clear for him to burn at will.<br>
<br>
There are not many mobs where manaburn makes sense, but there are a few cases where I belive it helps.<br>
<br>
 <p><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-size:medium;"><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Valas Defai</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.insidiousblood.net/"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-size:x-small;">A member of Insidious Blood</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=211027&amp;resize=true" target="top"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-size:xx-small;">My Magelo</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ravilicuslolf>Ravilicus LoLF</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 731<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/23/03 9:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Manaburn</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>There are not many mobs where manaburn makes sense, but there are a few cases where I belive it helps<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I actually thought this for a while after the nerf patch myself, and while I definately think the effect isn't as potent anymore, I feel it is very much worth having on many encounters.<br>
<br>
The fact of the matter is, that with Sufficient AA abilities, Focus gear making my regular nukes extremely efficient, a nuke item and/or Mana Robe, a horse or drogmor (for outdoor encounters where they are feasible), FT gear, C5, Bot9, Mana Song, Familiar, Spiritual Dominion, Force Shield, Mod Rod, Harvest, Harvest of Druzzil, and SK or Necro group mana from taps depending on party makeup, I have more than enough mana available for continuous nuking even after a good Mana Burn.<br>
<br>
On fast a furious fights this is extremely powerful, on fights where aggro is a PITA (like Seru) it can also be beneficial as it allows you to do a large aggro free nuke, then regain mana while you let the MT thoroughly piss off the target.<br>
<br>
Mana Burn itself isn't all that great, but if you can manage to get sufficiently high mana regen and efficient nukes, it basically equates to a large, aggro free blast.<br>
<br>
Personally, I am psyched to have retrained it again (after I got 125+ AA, at 152 points currently), and I wish there was a skill to lower the refresh timer on it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=27052.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=27052.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=27052.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=27052.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=27052.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=27052.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option 